  "opening_lines": [
    {
      "line": 1,
      "text": "Deep Evolution ¢ Seva: Compassion in Action"
    },
    {
      "line": 2,
      "text": "Army Green: Retooling the Military"
    },
    {
      "line": 5,
      "text": "OLE EARTH:"
    },
    {
      "line": 8,
      "text": ": ACCESS TO TOOLS & IDEAS As nO"
    },
    {
      "line": 11,
      "text": "| ii)"
    },
    {
      "line": 12,
      "text": "2c |"
    },
    {
      "line": 15,
      "text": "AT THE BEGINNING OF"
    },
    {
      "line": 16,
      "text": "the twentieth Century"
    },
    {
      "line": 19,
      "text": "physicists who aspired to understand the"
    },
    {
      "line": 22,
      "text": "machinery of the cosmos ended up creating devices for"
    },
    {
      "line": 23,
      "text": "burning civilizations. And now the Faustian bargain has appeared"
    },
    {
      "line": 26,
      "text": "again, at the end of the century and millennium, promising the grail of"
    },
    {
      "line": 27,
      "text": "knowledge to a new kind of scientist - the computational biologist."
    },
    {
      "line": 28,
      "text": "“Applied evolution” is what Kevin Kelly calls this whole new way of"
    },
    {
      "line": 31,
      "text": "applying nature’s magic tricks to human needs. The time has come for"
    },
    {
      "line": 32,
      "text": "people outside the artificial-life labs in New Mexico, Michigan, and"
    },
    {
      "line": 33,
      "text": "Massachusetts to understand the coming biological revolution."
    },
    {
      "line": 36,
      "text": "Computational biology is related"
    },
    {
      "line": 37,
      "text": "to - but goes beyond - conven-"
    },
    {
      "line": 38,
      "text": "tional bio-engineering, because it"
    },
    {
      "line": 39,
      "text": "aims to discover the processes by"
    },
    {
      "line": 40,
      "text": "which the evolutionary drive"
    },
    {
      "line": 41,
      "text": "works its magic, then to apply"
    },
    {
      "line": 42,
      "text": "those powers in an amplified, ac-"
    },
    {
      "line": 43,
      "text": "celerated, focused manner."
    },
    {
      "line": 46,
      "text": "Life is a certain kind of pattern, a"
    },
    {
      "line": 47,
      "text": "pattern-reading and pattern-mak-"
    },
    {
      "line": 48,
      "text": "ing pattern; whether that pattern"
    },
    {
      "line": 49,
      "text": "is incarnated in DNA or instanti-"
    },
    {
      "line": 50,
      "text": "ated in computer algorithms, the"
    },
    {
      "line": 51,
      "text": "principles that cause complex"
    },
    {
      "line": 52,
      "text": "forms to evolve from simpler ones"
    },
    {
      "line": 53,
      "text": "seem to apply to silicon as well as"
    },
    {
      "line": 54,
      "text": "carbon. The scientists who crack"
    },
    {
      "line": 55,
      "text": "evolution’s code will have opened"
    },
    {
      "line": 56,
      "text": "the portals to powers far greater"
    },
    {
      "line": 57,
      "text": "than the energies at the heart of"
    },
    {
      "line": 58,
      "text": "the atom."
    },
    {
      "line": 61,
      "text": "It looks as if something even more"
    },
    {
      "line": 62,
      "text": "powerful than thermonuclear"
    }
  ]
}